<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8345352>
    dc:description "FIGURES 20–29. Lomechusoides inflatus Zetterstedt, 1828. 20, Lomechusoides mariae Palm, 1949, male lectotype, dorsal habitus; 21, L. mariae, male lectotype, pronotum in dorsal view (L: 0.90 mm, W: 1.35 mm); 22, L. mariae, male paralectotype, aedeagus, lateral view; 23, L. mariae, male paralectotype, aedeagus, ventral view; 24, L. mariae, male lectotype, metaventral process; 25, L. mariae, male paralectotype, apex of paramere; 26, L. inflatus, female holotype, spermatheca; 27, L. mariae, female paralectotype, spermatheca, (locality: Kihlangi); 28, L. mariae, female, spermatheca (locality: Soppero); 29, L. inflatus, male, antennomeres III–IV, (locality: Kihlangi). Scale bars in mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8345352/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

